    "lyrics": {
      "text": "Be quick to an-tic-i-pate our foes ere we be en-slaved by them that blas-pheme Thee and that men-ace us with their threats, O mer-ci-ful Christ our God; by Thy Cross de-feat them that op-pose us that they may know how might-y is the faith of Or-tho-dox Chris-tians, through Thy pure Moth-er’s prayers for us all, O on-ly Friend of man.\n\nO on-ly Friend__ of man.___"
